div.div: Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu 3rd Season
Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Psychological, Romance, Thriller

The third season of Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu. A year has passed since Subarus victory at the Sanctuary. He savors a life of fulfillment while Emilias camp stands united for the royal selectionuntil a fateful letter arrives. Anastasia, a royal selection candidate, has invited Emilia to the Watergate City of Priestella. But as the party begins its journey, crisis stirs beneath the surface and Subaru meets a cruel fate once again. (Source: Crunchyroll) Notes: The first episode has an extended runtime of ~90 minutes, and received an early premiere at Anime Expo on July 5, 2024.
The second season of Princess Connect! Re:Dive.
Comedy, Drama, Romance, Slice of Life

"What am I doing?" Yuuhi Nagi's high school life is already halfway over, but he still doesn't have any dreams, ambitions, or even friends in his class! Every day is boring, until he's suddenly in danger of getting held back! A bittersweet high school drama made up of 4 potential grade repeaters with the worst grades in the class and 1 student acting as their teacher!
(Source: Pocket Comics)

When Se-Yeong wakes from his coma, he realizes hes lost everything. His parents are dead, having set themselves on fire to bring attention to how Se-Yeong was bullied by his rich peers in school. But from what he can gather, the whole lot of themeight in totalhave gone back to their normal lives without consequences thanks to having such rich and powerful parents. Filled with anger and regret, Se-Yeong locks himself up in the highest-up, rooftop apartment of the building his parents have left him, shutting himself away from the rest of the world. But strange things start happening; he finds a giant burning sword on the rooftop, and theres a voice in his head, whispering to fight Se-Yeong thought hed lost everything, but looks like his revenge is just beginning now (Source: Lezhin US, edited)
